OL,3,CCampaigners warn stretch of river is
OL,4,C'dying' due to 4x4s driving through
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News Meridian's Harry Acton
OL,7,Freports from the River Meon at
OL,8,FDroxford.
OL,10,FA stretch of road that runs through
OL,11,Fthe River Meon near Droxford should
OL,12,Fclose, campaigners have said.
OL,14,FThe route, known as the T189 Mill
OL,15,FLane, passes through around 200m of
OL,16,Fthe river, and is used by motorists
OL,17,Fall year round.
