OL,3,CCampaigners warn stretch of river is
OL,4,C'dying' due to 4x4s driving through
OL,6,FHowever, concerns have been raised
OL,7,Fover the health of the stretch of
OL,8,Fwaterway, with locals warning nature
OL,9,Fis being put at risk by drivers.
OL,11,FThey say that part of the river is
OL,12,Feffectively 'dead', with very little
OL,13,Fweed growth and animal activity found
OL,14,Fin the area, due to 4x4s driving
OL,15,Fthrough it for fun.
OL,17,FPaul Vignaux, from The Test and Itchen
OL,18,FAssociation, is among environmental
OL,19,Fgroups concerned about this stretch of
OL,20,Fthe Meon.
