OL,3,CCampaigners warn stretch of river is
OL,4,C'dying' due to 4x4s driving through
OL,6,F"This is a special area of
OL,7,Fconservation... It's a compensation
OL,8,Fhabitat", he told ITV Meridian.
OL,10,F"It's a protected space... The
OL,11,Fconstant traffic up and down will be
OL,12,Fcompacting the gravels and ripping up
OL,13,Fthe weed, and that stops spawning.
OL,15,F"It basically takes out the bottom of
OL,16,Fthe food chain because all the insect
OL,17,Flife, the invertebrates, depend on the
OL,18,Fweed."
