OL,3,CCampaigners warn stretch of river is
OL,4,C'dying' due to 4x4s driving through
OL,6,FPam Eastwood is the chair of the River
OL,7,FMeon Conservation Volunteers and says
OL,8,Fshe has witnessed the health of the
OL,9,Friver decline.
OL,11,F"What we're asking the four-wheel
OL,12,Fdrivers to do is waive their right",
OL,13,Fshe said. "They do have a right to be
OL,14,Fhere, but they also have a
OL,15,Fresponsibility to the environment as a
OL,16,Fhabitat and to other people who want
OL,17,Fto use the river in safety.
OL,19,F"We're asking to stop this now so that
OL,20,Fthe river can have an opportunity to
OL,21,Fregenerate. "
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
