OL,3,CCampaigners warn stretch of river is
OL,4,C'dying' due to 4x4s driving through
OL,6,FWatch: Pam Eastwood is urging drivers
OL,7,Fto be conscious of the environment.
OL,9,FNearby roads already link both ends of
OL,10,FMill Lane, without the need to pass
OL,11,Fthrough the river. Which campaigners
OL,12,Fargue makes driving through the river
OL,13,Fnecessary.
OL,15,FThe route is also realistically only
OL,16,Faccessible to 4x4s due to the depth of
OL,17,Fthe water.
OL,19,FHowever, motoring groups believe that
OL,20,Fthe T189 should stay as a highway,
OL,21,Fwith drivers able to use it.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
