OL,4,C'dying' due to 4x4s driving through
OL,6,F"I think the whole conversation needs
OL,7,Fto be framed in the understanding that
OL,8,Fthis is first and foremost a road", he
OL,9,Fsaid. "Although visually what your
OL,10,Fcamera is looking at looks like a
OL,11,Friver, and it is a river, it's
OL,12,Feffectively a ford which is a
OL,13,Fcontinuation of the road.
OL,15,F"Because it's a road, there is a right
OL,16,Ffor anybody to drive it at any time.
