OL,6,F"And also because it's a road, it's
OL,7,Frecognised by the local highways'
OL,8,Fauthority, which in this case is
OL,9,FHampshire, and that also is incumbent
OL,10,Fon them to keep that road open and
OL,11,Faccessible."
OL,13,FWatch: Steve Banks-Smith from the
OL,14,FGreen Lane Association stresses the
OL,15,Fimportance of rural roads.
OL,17,FAny decision will have to be taken by
OL,18,FHampshire County Council, with a
OL,19,Fspokesperson confirming the authority
OL,20,Fis aware of the issue in Droxford.
