OL,3,CCampaigners warn stretch of river is
OL,4,C'dying' due to 4x4s driving through
OL,6,FThey said: "We recognise that this is
OL,7,Fan important chalk stream habitat
OL,8,Fwhich, at the same time, is legally a
OL,9,F'publicly maintainable highway'
OL,10,Fallowing access rights.
OL,12,FWe are, therefore, actively working
OL,13,Fwith all parties involved, including
OL,14,Fpositive discussions with South Downs
OL,15,FNational Park, to come to a resolution
OL,16,Fas soon as practicable."
OL,18,FDroxford is also within the South
OL,19,FDowns National Park, which has a
OL,20,Fseparate governing authority.
