OL,6,FIt is powerless to impose traffic
OL,7,Frestrictions, but can work with local
OL,8,Fcouncils to address environmental harm.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "The South Downs
OL,11,FNational Park Authority is working
OL,12,Fwith Hampshire County Council as a
OL,13,Fmatter of urgency, to request their
OL,14,Fintervention due to concern relating
OL,15,Fto the ongoing degradation of the
OL,16,FRiver Meon at the T189 Mill Lane
OL,17,F"splash route".
