OL,6,F"While the SDNPA holds certain
OL,7,Fdiscretionary powers, we cannot
OL,8,Fregulate traffic on the surfaced
OL,9,Fsections of Mill Lane. As the Highway
OL,10,Fand Traffic Authority, Hampshire
OL,11,FCounty Council is the body with the
OL,12,Fstatutory responsibility to implement
OL,13,Fa comprehensive Traffic Regulation
OL,14,FOrder (TRO) where environmental harm
OL,15,Fis occurring.
OL,17,F"The Authority stands ready to assist
OL,18,FHampshire County Council."
